data.description: Brand NEW energy-efficient townhome ready July 2021! The Pompano model boasts all block construction with impact windows + spray foam insulation, 1485 sf with 3 bedrooms, flexible loft and walk-in laundry room on 2nd floor, 2.5 baths and a 1-car garage! Open floorplan with kitchen island.  Modern white shaker cabinets, white quartz countertops, 12"x 24" gray tile flooring, and neutral beige carpet is included in our Sleek Package. Seaside is a gated community that will have a total of 75 townhomes, pool and cabana, just 1.3 miles from downtown Stuart! Very convenient location and great schools in Martin County. Known for their energy-efficient features, our homes help you live a healthier and quieter lifestyle while saving thousands of dollars on utility bills.
